General.Name: Jubilant Flame International Ltd
General.Description: Jubilant Flame International, Ltd. provides technical support services for the development of nutrition food products in the United States. The company's nutritional oriented foods, such as sea-buckthourn and organic spouting powder. The company was formerly known as Jiu Feng Investment Hong Kong Ltd. and changed its name to Jubilant Flame International, Ltd. in May 2015. Jubilant Flame International, Ltd. was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Shanghai, China.
